---
// Quote banner section
---

<section class="section--primary quote-banner">
  <h3>Pensé que sería un cliente,</h3>
  <p>me he convertido en un amigo</p>
</section>

<style>
  .quote-banner {
    min-height: 250px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 64px 16px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a3865 0%, #2a4a7a 100%);
    color: #fff;
  }
  
  .quote-banner h3 {
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    color: #fff;
  }
  
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .quote-banner h3 {
      font-size: 36px;
    }
  }
  
  .quote-banner p {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 900;
    margin: 0;
    color: #95cca5;
  }
  
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .quote-banner p {
      font-size: 28px;
    }
  }
</style>
